**解法一**

目标元素多时

```java
public int removeElement(int[] nums, int val) {
    int i = 0;
    for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++) {
        if (nums[j] != val) {
            nums[i++] = nums[j];
        }
    }
    return i;
}
```

目标元素少时

```java
public int removeElement2(int[] nums, int val) {
    int i = 0;
    int n = nums.length;
    while (i < n) {
        if (nums[i] == val) {
            nums[i] = nums[--n];
        } else {
            i++;
        }
    }
    return n;
}
```

