**Follow up:**

Could you optimize your algorithm to use only *O*(*k*) extra space?

```java
 public List<Integer> getRow(int rowIndex) {
        List<Integer> res=new ArrayList<>();
        long cur=1;
        res.add((int)cur);
        for(int i=1;i<=rowIndex;i++){
            cur=cur*(rowIndex-i+1)/i;
            res.add((int)cur);
        }
        return res;
 }
