**解法一**

拒绝采样，两次Rand7()拒绝大于40的情况

```java
public int rand10() {
    int a,b,idx;
    do{
        a=rand7();
        b=rand7();
        idx=a+(b-1)*7;
    }while(idx>40);
    return 1+(idx-1)%10;
}
```

