### InstanceHolder

```java
public class SingleGraceful {
    private SingleGraceful(){

    }
    //private静态内部类
    private static class InstanceHolder{
        //只会被初始化一次
        private final static SingleGraceful instance=new SingleGraceful();
    }

    public static SingleGraceful getInstance(){
